  - "6 Blunt arms Bladed (d6 in melee)\nKNIGHTED BY...\nThe Roaming Seer\nVIG 10,
    CLA 14, SPI 6, 4 GD\n\u2022 A tall cloaked figure, leaving a trail of\nsand in
    his footsteps.\n\u2022 Will not offer any guidance to visitors, but\noffers to
    accompany any Knights he\ndeems worthy. He is demanding, slow,\nand cryptic,
    but offers clear guidance\nwhen it matters most.\n\u2022 Wants to see everything
    for himself."
